      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-7.centered
            %h3 WHAT IS ShGR?
            %p Pronounced "Sugar" - This is an app that promotes tangible giving by connecting the three major facets of the community- Supporters, Charitable Organizations, and Grocers.  With specific lists from local shelters, you can make a true difference in the lives of people in your community by purchasing just one extra item next time you go grocery shopping.

          .col-lg-5.centered
